  "content": "<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_DCL-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL is a SEPARATE artifact from the CDS view — file extension .asr</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>The CDS view must have @AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL uses ASPECT = PVZM to define mapping between fields and auth objects</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Implicit access control is based on PFCG authorization object fields</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>DCL can restrict: SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE (per operation)</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_DCL-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 700 420\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arrow-red\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#EF4444\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arrow-green\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#22C55E\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">DCL — Access Control Flow</text>\n\n  <!-- User Request -->\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"55\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">User Request</text>\n  <text x=\"100\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">(ABAP / OData)</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"220\" y2=\"80\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- CDS View -->\n  <rect x=\"225\" y=\"55\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"305\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">CDS View</text>\n  <text x=\"305\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">@AccessControl.authorizationCheck</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"385\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"425\" y2=\"80\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- DCL Check -->\n  <rect x=\"430\" y=\"55\" width=\"200\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"78\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">DCL: Access Control</text>\n  <text x=\"530\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Define PCD / PFCG mapping</text>\n\n  <!-- Decision diamond -->\n  <polygon points=\"350,145 430,185 350,225 270,185\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"189\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Access</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"203\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Granted?</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"350\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"350\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Granted path -->\n  <line x1=\"430\" y1=\"185\" x2=\"550\" y2=\"185\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-green)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"555\" y=\"165\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"625\" y=\"182\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Data Returned</text>\n  <text x=\"625\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Filtered set</text>\n\n  <!-- Denied path -->\n  <line x1=\"270\" y1=\"185\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"185\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-red)\"/>\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"165\" width=\"135\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"87\" y=\"182\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">No Data</text>\n  <text x=\"87\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Empty / suppressed</text>\n\n  <!-- DCL syntax example -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"260\" width=\"600\" height=\"140\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">DCL Syntax Example</text>\n\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"310\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748b\">@MappingRole: true</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"325\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748b\">define role ZPRAC_TRAVEL_SALES {</text>\n  <text x=\"90\" y=\"340\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748b\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</text>\n  <text x=\"110\" y=\"355\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748b\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( org_value, 'S_CARRID', 'ACTVT' );</text>\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"370\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#64748b\">}</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">PFCG authorization objects → ABAP roles → CDS row-level security</text>\n</svg></div>",
  "tags": [
    "cds-views"
  ],
  "details": "<p class=\"mb-2\">WHAT IS DCL?</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DCL (Data Control Language) is a CDS artifact (.asr file) that</p><p class=\"mb-2\">defines row-level security for CDS views. It works with PFCG</p><p class=\"mb-2\">authorization objects to filter data per user.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DCL SYNTAX OVERVIEW:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'Access control for ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@MappingRole: true</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">COMMON DCL PATTERNS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌──────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Pattern                          │ When to use                    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├──────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ grant select ... where ...       │ Standard row-level restriction │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ grant all on ...                 │ Full access (admin purpose)    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ inherit access for ...           │ Delegate to underlying view    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ aspect pfcg_auth(...)            │ Map CDS field to PFCG auth obj │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ $sy_user_agr()                   │ User's authorization values    │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└──────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — INHERIT ACCESS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Delegate access control to an underlying view. The current view</p><p class=\"mb-2\">inherits the DCL restrictions from its data source automatically.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'DCL for ZPRAC_CDS_VIEW_ON_VIEW (inherits)'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@MappingRole: true</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_VON_V_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_VIEW_ON_VIEW {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant inherited access for select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE;</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — DEFINE ASPECT:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Create reusable authorization conditions for multiple roles.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@EndUserText.label: 'Aspect for Agency authorization'</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define aspect ZPRAC_ASPECT_AGENCY {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() )</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect ZPRAC_ASPECT_AGENCY;</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — CONDITIONAL GRANTS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Grant different access levels based on user authorization values.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_TRAVEL_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant insert, update, delete on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '01,02', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — INSTANCE-BASED ACCESS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Restrict access to specific instances based on field values.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Multiple WHERE conditions can be combined with AND/OR.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() )</p><p class=\"mb-2\">and (Status) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV_STATUS, ACTVT = '03', STATUS = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">ADVANCED DCL — ACCESS POLICIES FOR READ/WRITE:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">Use different PFCG activities for read vs write access.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">define role ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE_AC {</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant select on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '03', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant insert on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '01', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">grant update on ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE</p><p class=\"mb-2\">where (AgencyId) = aspect pfcg_auth( /DMO/TRV, ACTVT = '02', AGENCY = $sy_user_agr() );</p><p class=\"mb-2\">}</p><p class=\"mb-2\">BEST PRACTICE RULES:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Rule                                           │ Reason                     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Always use @AccessControl.authorizationCheck   │ Required for DCL to apply  │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use #CHECK at consumption layer                │ Enforces row-level security│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use inherit access for VDM layer stacking      │ Avoids DCL duplication     │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Use define aspect for reusable conditions      │ DRY principle              │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Grant different activities per operation       │ Principle of least privilege│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Never use DCL on private/interface views       │ Internal views don't need it│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Always run unit tests with DISABLE_DCL         │ Avoid flaky tests          │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/dcl-flow.svg</p>",
